app, ss = basic_ss
test_client = SocketIOTestClient(app, ss.socketio, namespace=ss.namespace)
assert len(ss.connection_subscriptions) == 0
test_client.emit('message', json.dumps({'type': SUBSCRIPTION_START,
    'payload': 'foo', 'id': 1, 'query': 'query test{ testString }',
    'variables': 'baz'}), namespace=ss.namespace)
assert len(ss.connection_subscriptions) == 1
test_client.emit('message', json.dumps({'type': SUBSCRIPTION_END, 'payload':
    'foo', 'id': 1}), namespace=ss.namespace)
assert len(ss.connection_subscriptions) == 0
